item.title: My Roots
item.author: jacquetped@gmail.com (Prince JACQUET)
item.description: Welcome to the page where you can discover the roots of who I am today. This is where I share the groups and individuals that have influenced my journey and shaped my character. Groups One group that has had a profound impact on my personal and professional growth is the … TIM UPS-INSA (￣▽￣)ノ . This student association focuses on building fuel-efficient cars from scratch and has provided me with an environment for continuous learning.
